OL,3,CNorthern Ireland barristers strike
OL,4,Cover fees
OL,6,FCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland have gone on strike as part of
OL,8,Fa dispute over the payment of legal
OL,9,Faid fees.
OL,11,FThey've voted to not take on any new
OL,12,FCategory A Crown Court cases, which
OL,13,Finclude those of murder and
OL,14,Fmanslaughter.
OL,16,FBarristers will also refuse
OL,17,Finstructions in any retrials as a
OL,18,Fresult of hung juries or appeals.
OL,20,FA protest took place outside the Royal
OL,21,FCourts of Justice on Monday morning.
