OL,6,FChairman of the Bar Council of
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Donal Lunny KC, said
OL,8,Fhe and his colleagues regard strike
OL,9,Faction as a last resort.
OL,11,F"The Bar Council has, for many months,
OL,12,Fbeen exploring every possible
OL,13,Falternative measure and has
OL,14,Fconsistently called for urgent action
OL,15,Ffrom the Department of Justice to
OL,16,Favoid any withdrawal of service taking
OL,17,Fplace," he said.
