OL,6,F"This is now a grave situation where
OL,7,Fwe have been forced to highlight
OL,8,Fpublicly that the current system is
OL,9,Fwholly unsustainable due to a lack of
OL,10,Ffunding, engagement, and action, from
OL,11,Fthe Department of Justice.
OL,13,F"Barristers are independent, self-
OL,14,Femployed practitioners, many of whom
OL,15,Fare not just struggling but are at
OL,16,Fbreaking point. Our consistent
OL,17,Fwarnings to the department have gone
OL,18,Funheeded, and the foreseeable result
OL,19,Fis a serious access to justice crisis."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@gO]
