OL,6,FHe added: "Today's initial strike
OL,7,Faction has not been taken lightly, it
OL,8,Fis very much a last resort.
OL,10,F"It is a regrettable but necessary
OL,11,Fmeasure to preserve the viability of
OL,12,Fthe system of Criminal Legal Aid as a
OL,13,Fvital public service.
