OL,6,F"Criminal cases are becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly complex, court delays are
OL,8,Fat chronic proportions despite
OL,9,Fcriminal barristers working at 130%
OL,10,Fcapacity, Crown Court fees have not
OL,11,Fbeen increased in almost 20 years and
OL,12,Fbarristers are forced to wait three to
OL,13,Ffour months to be paid.
OL,15,F"We understand the concern this will
OL,16,Fcause to victims and those seeking
OL,17,Fjustice in relation to serious crimes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
