OL,6,F"However, victims should be in no
OL,7,Fdoubt that it is the department's
OL,8,Fprolonged inaction that has brought us
OL,9,Fto today's crisis.
OL,11,F"An effective, properly funded
OL,12,Fcriminal justice system is as
OL,13,Fimportant, if not more important, to
OL,14,Fvictims as it is to everyone else
OL,15,Finvolved in that system.
