OL,6,FIn a statement to the Assembly on
OL,7,FMonday afternoon, Justice Minister
OL,8,FNaomi Long said the action by criminal
OL,9,Fpractitioners "reflects frustrations
OL,10,Fwith the system", adding that she
OL,11,F"shares those frustrations",
OL,12,Fdescribing her department as
OL,13,F"consistently underfunded".
OL,15,FShe told MLAs she has undertaken a
OL,16,Fdetailed assessment of how resources
OL,17,Fare currently used and of reform
OL,18,Fopportunities, and will update the
OL,19,FAssembly on that in the coming weeks.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@PO]sD@AOUsD@[O]uD@AOUuD@ZO]
