OL,6,F"Pressure on the system is at an all-
OL,7,Ftime high and increasing," said Ms
OL,8,FLong.
OL,10,F"In 2023/24 the Legal Services Agency
OL,11,Fpaid out approximately #114m to legal
OL,12,Fprofessionals, the highest level in
OL,13,Fthe history of legal aid.
